# data/prospects.db is intentionally tracked (not ignored): the scheduled
# GitHub Actions workflow commits fresh enrichment results here, and
# Streamlit Community Cloud auto-redeploys on push — that's what makes the
# dashboard "always on" without running a dedicated server. See
# .github/workflows/refresh.yml.
